metadata.name: #1 Frank van Dork
metadata.description:
Evil Dorkis are creeps, weirdos and lurkers, created the old-fashioned way with pen and coloured pencil on paper, scanned and edited to make 4724 evil clones. Each Evil Dorkis has a trait-matching counterpart in the original collection. Bringing good and evil together will have its rewards. 

We are a team of NFT dorks dedicated to the NFT community. We're building an inclusive and diverse society - celebrating what makes us all unique dorks. 

We Are Dorkis grant the owner of this NFTs, a non-exclusive, royalty-free license to make, use and sell their Evil Dorkis worldwide.
